title: Class Fitsugar
descriptionHTML:
Class FitSugar is the #1 real-time workout show online, offering a unique mix of fun, inspirational, and on-trend workouts you can do anytime, anywhere. With over 6 million YouTube subscribers, and over 275 million views in 2020 alone, Class Fitsugar relaunched in 2021 with a bold, new look.
